headline: Redburn Upgrades Charles River Laboratories (CRL) to Buy, Cuts PT
summary: On May 23, Redburn Atlantic turned bullish on Charles River Laboratories International, Inc. (NYSE:CRL) as it upgraded its stock from “Neutral” to “Buy,” despite marginally reducing the price objective to $182 from $188.
